        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Assistance for Rural Community Hospitals Act of 2022 or the ARCH Act of 2022</b></p> <p>This bill extends certain payment adjustments for Medicare-dependent hospitals and low-volume hospitals until the end of FY2027 (the adjustments currently expire at the end of FY2022).</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
